(1846, NULL, 'Modem VDSL/ADSL2+ & FTTH Draytek Vigor 2860', 'Modem VDSL-ADSL2+ & FTTH Draytek Vigor 2860', 'modem-vdsladls2-ftth-dratek-vigor-2860', 5, 88, '', '3964', 3350000, 0, 0, 0, '<div>\r\n	VDSL/ADSL2+ Router &amp; Load Balancing Router &nbsp;=&gt; 2 in 1</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- 1 port VDSL/ADSL2+ &amp; 1 GigaWAN (10/100/1000Mbps) connect to FTTH/ADSL, Load balancing &amp; Backup link.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- 6 Gigabite LAN port with VLAN, Rate Limit control.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- NAT throughput WAN2 upto 300Mbps</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- VPN sever with 32VPN tunnels (16 SSL VPN tunnels), 60Mbps VPN bandwith for IPSec. Easy for Branch-to-office, Teleworker- to-Office.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- Bandwith management &amp; Limit Session, QoS Function. Dynamic DNS; IP Alias for multi-NAT; Syslog, DNS cache &amp; proxy. IP base &amp; MAC add Internet Access Control.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- Central VPN Management (TR-069) for Vigor series.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- APM (AP Management): Central management for VigorAP (20 APs)</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- 2 USB port connect Mobile HDD for File Server, 3G/4G modem (WAN3, WAN4) or USB printer.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- Firewall security with NAT, DoS &amp; DDoS, DMZ, Packet Filtering, Multi Subnets.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- Web content filter with CSM (Content Security Management)</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- Web portal: URL direct or show Message</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- Smart monitor (30pc): Xem nội dung chat, email, web... của từng user tr&ecirc;n mạng</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- K&ecirc;nh thu&ecirc; ri&ecirc;ng: L3VPN/L2VPN, Leased line</div>\r\n', 0, 1, 0, 100, 0, 1, 1057, 7, 1, '2016-11-01 14:51:13', '2016-12-28 15:39:29'),
