Intel&reg; HD Graphics support:<br />\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x DisplayPorts, supporting a maximum resolution of 4096x2304@60 Hz<br />\r\n				*Support for DisplayPort 1.2 version.<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x DVI-D port, supporting a maximum resolution of 1920x1200@60 Hz<br />\r\n				*The DVI-D port does not support D-Sub connection by adapter.<br />\r\n				Maximum shared memory of 1024 MB</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				C&ocirc;ng nghệ đa card đồ họa</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				Support for 3-Way/2-Way AMD CrossFire&trade; and 2-Way NVIDIA&reg; SLI&trade; Technology</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				&Acirc;m thanh</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Realtek&reg; ALC1150 codec<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; High Definition Audio<br />\r\n				3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2/4/5.1/7.1-channel<br />\r\n				4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Support for S/PDIF Outc</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				LAN</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2 x Intel&reg; GbE LAN chips (10/100/1000 Mbit)<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Support for Teaming</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				Khe cắm mở rộng</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x PCI Express x16 slot, running at x16 (PCIEX16)<br />\r\n				* For optimum performance, if only one PCI Express graphics card is to be installed, be sure to install it in the PCIEX16 slot.<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x PCI Express x16 slot, running at x8 (PCIEX8)<br />\r\n				3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x PCI Express x16 slot, running at x4 (PCIEX4)<br />\r\n				* The PCIEX4 slot shares bandwidth with the SATA3 0/1 connectors.<br />\r\n				When the PCIEX4 slot is installed with a x4 or above card, the SATA 3 0/1 connectors becomes unavailable.<br />\r\n				4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x PCI Express x1 slot<br />\r\n				* The PCIEX1 slot shares bandwidth with the SATA3 2/3 and U2_32G connectors. When the U2_32G connector is installed with an U.2 device, the PCIEX1 and SATA3 2/3 connectors become unavailable.<br />\r\n				(All of the PCI Express slots conform to PCI Express 3.0 standard.)<br />\r\n				<ol>\r\n					<li value=\"5\">\r\n						2 x PCI slot</li>\r\n				</ol>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				Giao diện lưu trữ</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				Chipset:<br />\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x M.2 connector (Socket 3, M key, type 2242/2260/2280/22110 SATA and PCIe x4/x2 SSD support)<br />\r\n				* If the iRSTe Support item in BIOS Setup is set to Enabled, the RAID function will become unavailable when an M.2 PCIe SSD is installed.<br />\r\n				(Refer to Chapter 2, &quot;BIOS Setup,&quot; &quot;Peripherals,&quot; for more information.)<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x U.2 connector<br />\r\n				3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2 x SATA Express connectors<br />\r\n				4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6 x SATA 6Gb/s connectors (SATA3 0~5)<br />\r\n				5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Support for RAID 0, RAID 1, RAID 5, and RAID 10<br />\r\n				* Refer to &quot;1-9 Internal Connectors,&quot; for the supported configurations with the U.2, M.2, SATA Express, and SATA connectors.<br />\r\n				ASMedia&reg; ASM1061 chip:<br />\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2 x SATA 6Gb/s connectors (GSATA3 6~7), supporting AHCI mode only</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				USB</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				Chipset+Intel&reg; USB 3.1 Controller:<br />\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x USB Type-C&trade; port on the back panel, with USB 3.1 support<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x USB 3.1 Type-A port (red) on the back panel<br />\r\n				Chipset:<br />\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6 x USB 3.0/2.0 ports (3 ports on the back panel, 1 ports onboard, 2 ports available through the internal USB headers)<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6 x USB 2.0/1.1 ports (2 ports on the back panel, 4 ports available through the internal USB headers)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				Kết nối I/O b&ecirc;n trong</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x 24-pin ATX main power connector<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x 8-pin ATX 12V power connector<br />\r\n				3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x power information detection header (PMBUS)<br />\r\n				4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x U.2 connector<br />\r\n				5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x M.2 Socket 3 connector<br />\r\n				6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2 x SATA Express connectors<br />\r\n				7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 8 x SATA 6Gb/s connectors<br />\r\n				8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2 x SATA power headers (SATA_DOM)<br />\r\n				9.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2 x SATA detection headers (SATA_SGP)<br />\r\n				10.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x CPU fan header<br />\r\n				11.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x water cooling fan header (CPU_OPT)<br />\r\n				12.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x system fan header (SYS_FAN2)<br />\r\n				13.&nbsp;&nbsp; 3 x system fan/water cooling pump headers (SYS_FAN1/3/4_PUMP)<br />\r\n				14.&nbsp;&nbsp; 3 x smart fan mode control jumpers<br />\r\n				15.&nbsp;&nbsp; 3 x temperature sensor headers<br />\r\n				16.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x front panel header<br />\r\n				17.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x front panel audio header<br />\r\n				18.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x USB 3.0/2.0 header<br />\r\n				19.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x USB 3.0/2.0 port (USB30_OB)<br />\r\n				20.&nbsp;&nbsp; 2 x USB 2.0/1.1 headers<br />\r\n				21.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x S/PDIF Out header<br />\r\n				22.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x Trusted Platform Module (TPM) header<br />\r\n				23.&nbsp;&nbsp; 2 x serial port headers<br />\r\n				24.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x Thunderbolt&trade; add-in card connector<br />\r\n				25.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x Clear CMOS jumper<br />\r\n				26.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x power button<br />\r\n				27.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x reset button<br />\r\n				28.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x Clear CMOS button<br />\r\n				29.&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x BIOS switch</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				Kết nối bảng ph&iacute;a sau</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x PS/2 keyboard/mouse port<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x DVI-D port<br />\r\n				3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x DisplayPort<br />\r\n				4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x USB Type-C&trade; port, with USB 3.1 support<br />\r\n				5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x USB 3.1 Type-A port (red)<br />\r\n				6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3 x USB 3.0/2.0 ports<br />\r\n				7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2 x USB 2.0/1.1 ports<br />\r\n				8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2 x RJ-45 ports<br />\r\n				9.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 x optical S/PDIF Out connector<br />\r\n				10.&nbsp;&nbsp; 5 x audio jacks (Center/Subwoofer Speaker Out, Rear Speaker Out, Line In, Line Out, Mic In)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				Điều khiển I/O</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				iTE&reg; I/O Controller Chip</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				Theo d&otilde;i phần cứng</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; System voltage detection<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; CPU/System/Chipset temperature detection<br />\r\n				3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; CPU/CPU OPT/System fan (pump) speed detection<br />\r\n				4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; CPU/System/Chipset overheating warning<br />\r\n				5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; CPU/CPU OPT/System fan (pump) fail warning<br />\r\n				6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; CPU/CPU OPT/System fan (pump) speed control<br />\r\n				* Whether the fan speed control function is supported will depend on the fan (pump) you install.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				BIOS</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2 x 128 Mbit flash<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Use of licensed AMI UEFI BIOS<br />\r\n				3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; PnP 1.0a, DMI 2.7, WfM 2.0, SM BIOS 2.7, ACPI 5.0</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				T&iacute;nh năng duy nhất</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Support for APP Center<br />\r\n				* Available applications in APP Center may vary by motherboard model. Supported functions of each application may also vary depending on motherboard specifications.<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; @BIOS<br />\r\n				3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ambient LED<br />\r\n				4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ON/OFF Charge<br />\r\n				5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; System Information Viewer<br />\r\n				6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Support for Q-Flash<br />\r\n				7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Support for Xpress Install</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				Hệ điều h&agrave;nh</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Support for Windows 10/8.1 64-bit<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Support for Windows 7 32-bit/64-bit<br />\r\n				* Please download the &quot;Windows USB Installation Tool&quot; from GIGABYTE&#39;s website and install it before installing Windows 7.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:181px;\">\r\n				Ghi ch&uacute;</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:420px;\">\r\n				1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Due to different Linux support condition provided by chipset vendors, please download Linux driver from chipset vendors&#39; website or 3rd party website.<br />\r\n				2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Most hardware/software vendors may no longer offer drivers to support Win9X/ME/2000/XP. If drivers are available from the vendors, we will update them on the GIGABYTE website.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1306, 1, 1, '2016-11-24 14:51:27', '2017-01-06 13:57:51'),
(2074, NULL, 'Dell Vostro 14 3468 - 70087405', 'Dell Vostro 14 3468 - 70087405', 'dell-vostro-14-3468-70087405', 2, 8, '', '3787', 10490000, 0, 9990000, 0, '<div>\r\n	<strong>Thiết kế th&acirc;n thiện, t&iacute;nh di động cao</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Laptop Dell Vostro 3468 70087405 l&agrave; một trong những chiếc m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh x&aacute;ch tay được h&atilde;ng Dell chăm ch&uacute;t v&agrave; đầu tư rất kỹ lưỡng. Ngo&agrave;i ra, m&aacute;y c&ograve;n c&oacute; thiết kế th&acirc;n thiện, đẹp mắt, m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh nhỏ gọn 14 inches, cấu h&igrave;nh mạnh mẽ c&ugrave;ng dung lượng pin 4 Cell, hệ thống b&agrave;n ph&iacute;m v&agrave; Touchpad tiện dụng..., cho người d&ugrave;ng thoải m&aacute;i trải nghiệm từ việc xử l&yacute; c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng việc văn ph&ograve;ng đến giải tr&iacute;, xem phim, nghe nhạc h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y. Thiết bị n&agrave;y được b&aacute;n với gi&aacute; kh&aacute; tốt, so với những d&ograve;ng sản phẩm kh&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n thị trường hiện nay.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Kiểu d&aacute;ng nhỏ gọn</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Sở hữu trọng lượng chỉ 2.0Kg, c&ugrave;ng k&iacute;ch thước chiều d&agrave;i: 345 mm, chiều rộng: 243 mm v&agrave; độ d&agrave;y: 23 mm, Laptop Dell Vostro 3468 70087405 c&oacute; vẻ ngo&agrave;i bắt mắt, kiểu d&aacute;ng nhỏ gọn, năng động, mang đến sự thuận tiện khi di chuyển cho người d&ugrave;ng. Bạn c&oacute; thể sắp xếp m&aacute;y trong t&uacute;i du lịch v&agrave; đem theo trong c&aacute;c chuyến c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	B&ecirc;n cạnh đ&oacute;, phần vỏ b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i của m&aacute;y được thiết kế cực kỳ chắc chắn v&agrave; cứng c&aacute;p, phủ t&ocirc;ng m&agrave;u đen mạnh mẽ, &iacute;t b&aacute;m bụi, hạn chế t&igrave;nh trạng b&aacute;m dấu v&acirc;n tay trong suốt qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh sử dụng.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Hiển thị h&igrave;nh ảnh sắc n&eacute;t</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh nhỏ gọn với k&iacute;ch thước 14 inches tr&ecirc;n chiếc Laptop Dell Vostro 3468 70087405 sẽ mang đến cho bạn những h&igrave;nh ảnh sắc n&eacute;t, trung thực, chi tiết, g&oacute;c nh&igrave;n rộng, m&agrave;u sắc cũng rất sống động v&agrave; nổi bật.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; thế, d&ograve;ng m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh x&aacute;ch tay Dell Vostro 3468 70087405 cũng hỗ trợ bạn rất nhiều khi xử l&yacute; c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng việc li&ecirc;n quan đến h&igrave;nh ảnh, đồng thời, cho bạn trải nghiệm khoảng thời gian xem phim, chơi game cực kỳ th&uacute; vị.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Cấu h&igrave;nh mạnh mẽ</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Kh&ocirc;ng chỉ chiếm cảm t&igrave;nh của người d&ugrave;ng nhờ vẻ ngo&agrave;i th&acirc;n thiện, m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh nhỏ gọn, chiếc Laptop Dell Vostro 3468 70087405 c&ograve;n g&acirc;y ấn tượng bởi bộ vi xử l&yacute; mạnh mẽ b&ecirc;n trong với Intel Core i3-7100U tốc độ 2.40GHz, đủ sức xử l&yacute; mượt m&agrave; c&aacute;c t&aacute;c vụ, hoạt động trơn tru v&agrave; &ecirc;m &aacute;i, hạn chế hiện tượng lag hay giật m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Đồng thời, với dung lượng RAM l&ecirc;n đến 4GB, ổ cứng l&ecirc;n đến 1TB, Laptop Dell Vostro 3468 70087405 ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n đ&aacute;p ứng được nhu cầu học tập của c&aacute;c bạn học sinh, sinh vi&ecirc;n, chạy tốt c&aacute;c ứng dụng văn ph&ograve;ng, phục vụ tốt cho nhu cầu chơi game hay lướt web th&ocirc;ng thường...</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Ngo&agrave;i ra, card đồ họa Intel HD Graphics cũng hỗ trợ bạn xem phim v&agrave; chơi game với chất lượng h&igrave;nh ảnh tốt, xử l&yacute; c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng việc li&ecirc;n quan đến đồ họa nhanh ch&oacute;ng hơn.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>B&agrave;n ph&iacute;m 